# MovieList — `src/hooks`

## Shape

- Prefer **`UseQueryResult<T>`**: **`data`**, **`loading`**, **`error`**, **`refetch`** for data hooks.
- Hooks call **`api/movies.ts`** (via **`client`** indirectly) — not raw axios.

## Search

- Debounce user input **400ms** using **`useRef`** + **`clearTimeout`** (stable cleanup).
- **Cancel or ignore stale** search responses when query/order changes (abort controller or explicit request id / “latest wins”).

## Boundaries

- **No navigation** (`navigation.navigate`, etc.) inside hooks — screens/nav handlers own routing.

## Detail and parallel loads

- For independent parallel sections (e.g. detail), orchestrate with **`Promise.allSettled`** and surface per-section loading/errors as specified in PSDs.
